  [ Roger Leigh ]
  * flash-kernel-installer postinst: Update FSCKFIX in
    /etc/default/fsck as well as /etc/default/rcS for backward
    compatibility.  The purpose is to use /etc/default/fsck for
    new installations. Closes: #694928

